title: Uriah Heep - Live at Sweden Rock Festival 2014 [FM] [FLAC]
description:
Uriah Heep recorded live at Sweden Rock Festival 2014.

FM broadcast received on a Revox B780 and recorded to a Revox B77 reel to reel.
Played back and recorded to computer with Audacity via external A/D.

The track has been trimmed, normalized and exported as FLAC (16bit/44kHz), nothing else.

Tracklist:
01 Sunrise
02 Stealin'
03 Can't Take That Away
04 Gypsy
05 Look At Yourself
06 July Morning
07 Lady In Black
08 Easy Livin'

Runtime: 56m 36s

NOTE: Swedish radio announcer speaks a couple of times during some intros
